data.description: Beautiful well maintained home in prestigious Shadow Creek Ranch Subdivision. Quiet neighborhood. Conveniently located near Broadway street, close to shopping, dining and entertainment. No back neighbors or directly in front of driveway. Walking distance to recreation park with pools and volley ball.  Open layout home. Enter to formals with crown molding and raised ceilings. Family room with a large fire place. Kitchen with granite countertops and plenty of cabinets. Good size master with double sinks on bath and large closet. Good size secondary bedrooms. Beautiful backyard with covered patio to enjoy.
